    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-12-11T16:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-12-11T16:00:00-05:00" n="7"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d7">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 861.00/804b</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Japan</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_MRS1" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Morris</hi>
                    </persName>)<note n="1" xml:id="d7fn1">The same, on the same date, to the
                        Minister in China.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-12-11T16:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 11, 1917, 4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>It is reported in the press that an announcement has been made by the Japanese
                    Government that Japanese forces are protecting Vladivostok. Please make discreet
                    but extensive inquiry and report by cable.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_LR1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
